      <title>日本央行行长河野太郎称央行需要提高利率来提振日元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/japan-s-kono-says-central-bank-needs-to-raise-rates-to-lift-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本一位主管数字机构的知名大臣为竞选首相留下了空间，他呼吁央行提高利率，以提高日元汇率，降低能源和食品成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/japan-s-kono-says-central-bank-needs-to-raise-rates-to-lift-yen</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 02:41:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FBI 协助调查曼谷豪华酒店六起神秘死亡事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/fbi-joins-probe-into-foreigner-deaths-at-bangkok-luxury-hotel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛表示，美国联邦调查局已联合泰国当局对曼谷一家豪华酒店六名外国人神秘死亡事件展开调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/fbi-joins-probe-into-foreigner-deaths-at-bangkok-luxury-hotel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 02:22:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普昔日对手称赞他，展现团结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/trump-s-former-rivals-unite-behind-him-at-republican-convention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[妮基·黑利曾称唐纳德·特朗普“完全精神错乱”且“卑微”。佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯此前曾表示，如果最“没用的共和党人”愿意“亲吻戒指”，这位前总统将拥抱他们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/trump-s-former-rivals-unite-behind-him-at-republican-convention</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 02:02:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前中情局官员被指控帮助韩国购买奢侈品包</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/ex-cia-official-accused-of-helping-south-korea-for-luxury-bags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国检察官起诉了一位前中央情报局朝鲜问题分析师，指控他离开该机构后为韩国担任间谍，以换取奢侈品和其他礼物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/ex-cia-official-accused-of-helping-south-korea-for-luxury-bags</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 00:36:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登计划提出最高法院改革，包括任期限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/biden-to-propose-supreme-court-reforms-including-term-limits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，总统乔·拜登计划公布可能大幅重塑最高法院的提案，包括对目前终身任职的法官的任期限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/biden-to-propose-supreme-court-reforms-including-term-limits</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 23:05:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的共和党扩大战场地图，警告不要陷入胜利圈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/gop-expands-battleground-map-as-party-warns-against-victory-lap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党全国委员会主席迈克尔·沃特利警告称，共和党本周结束正式的提名大会，民意调查预测前总统唐纳德·特朗普将在 11 月的选举中击败总统乔·拜登，因此不要自满。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/gop-expands-battleground-map-as-party-warns-against-victory-lap</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 22:20:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击事件后，拜登在全国有色人种协进会重回政治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/after-trump-shooting-biden-pivots-back-to-politics-at-naacp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，在谴责针对唐纳德·特朗普的暗杀企图的同时，还应该批评针对黑人的暴力行为，拒绝政治极端主义，支持枪支管制，因为他正重返竞选之路，为陷入困境的竞选寻找前进的道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/after-trump-shooting-biden-pivots-back-to-politics-at-naacp</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 22:13:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯和乌克兰将在阿联酋支持的协议中交换 180 名囚犯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/russia-and-ukraine-are-set-to-swap-180-prisoners-in-a-uae-backed-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，在阿联酋的促成下，俄罗斯和乌克兰将交换 180 名囚犯，这将是阿联酋今年主导的第六次囚犯交换。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/russia-and-ukraine-are-set-to-swap-180-prisoners-in-a-uae-backed-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 22:09:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党将在国王演讲中阐述新法律计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/labour-to-flesh-out-agenda-in-king-s-speech-outlining-legislative-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默将在周三的国王演讲中阐述英国新政府下一届议会会议的立法议程，并具体阐述工党从边境管制到吸烟等各个方面的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/labour-to-flesh-out-agenda-in-king-s-speech-outlining-legislative-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:16:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和黑莉团队周末讨论共和党全国委员会演讲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-haley-teams-spoke-over-weekend-about-rnc-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，前总统唐纳德·特朗普和妮基·黑利的团队——曾经是 2024 年大选的竞争对手——上周末谈到了她出席威斯康星州密尔沃基共和党全国代表大会的事情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-haley-teams-spoke-over-weekend-about-rnc-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 02:12:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
